====Noun====
[[Image:YellowPerch.jpg|right|thumb|200px|yellow perch (''Perca flavescens'')]]
{{en-noun|es|pl2=perch}}

# Any of the three species of [[spiny]]-[[fin|finned]] [[freshwater]] fish in the genus ''Perca''.
# Any of the about 200 related species of fish in the taxonomic family ''Percidae''.
# Several similar species in the [[order]] [[Perciformes]], such as the [[grouper]].

